 ensuring the well-being of these pioneers, revitalizing research culture, =
and developing talent.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>He declared that &#82=
20;science can be effective in the national welfare only as a member of a t=
eam, whether the conditions be peace or war. But </span><strong>without sci=
