><span>&#8221; It was simple. An enduring civilization was nothing without =
advances in how it gets things done. Stagnation meant death.&#160;&#160;</s=
pan></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; mar=
gin: 0 0 1em 0;">Bush&#8217;s objectives were reminiscent of American polic=
