-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>It's popular to p=
oint out that America doesn't build like we used to&#8212;during WW2, the S=
pace Race, or even the 1970s, when Apple and Genentech were both founded in=
 the year of our nation's Bicentennial. Something happened around 1973; pro=
