an> complained, &quot;the best minds of my generation are thinking about ho=
w to make people click ads.&quot; I&#8217;d argue that it was because we sa=
w a divergence in private-public collaboration as the government focused on=
 other domestic issues.</span></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>Neil deGrasse Tyson says i=
t best in his 2012 speech, </span><em>We Stopped Dreaming:</em></p><a href=
