es, strategies, and ecosystems conducive to building such ambitious, world-=
changing companies.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>My goal was and remains =
simple: </span><strong>to inspire at least one more person to take on such =
