the historic Bell Labs my entire life, and my mother is a survivor of 9/11 =
as she worked in the Twin Towers during that event (the North Tower to be s=
pecific). With those dual influences, I grew up wanting to use science and =
tech to do good for our country and the world. My book is a manifesto for t=
hat.&#160;</span></p><div class=3D"captioned-image-container-static" style=
