In turn, the media picked up his towering home runs and referred to them as=
 &#8220;moon shots.&#8221;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; =
line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Despite the transition in meaning fr=
om baseball to space exploration of the portmanteau &#8220;moonshot,&#8221;=
